3ï¸âƒ£ Domain Settings (Exam Favorite)

What Domains Control

- Who can:
  - Create workspaces
  - Create Lakehouses / Pipelines / Notebooks
- Isolation rules
- Governance policies
- Default workspace behavior

Why Domains Matter

- Apply across multiple workspaces
- Reduce admin effort
- Enforce consistent rules

Exam tip:
Enterprise-wide restriction â†’ Domain, not Workspace

